*Product team channels**: Focus on user-facing changes and business impact\\n- **Leadership channels**: Highlight progress on key initiatives and blockers\\n\"}]},\"isMeta\":true,\"uuid\":\"49834291-f4a4-4506-a23f-3241a625cb50\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T12:14:53.567Z\",\"sourceToolUseID\":\"toolu_01JzCNWhVRgfHNdncGGBuLB3\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"49834291-f4a4-4506-a23f-3241a625cb50\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"d77a9f03-1d5b-4e45-85cd-c5694a211420\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01GdVaYptosGMG395G4o5ePq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nLet me first check what version 0.4.7 corresponds to and find all changes since then.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1253,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":45180,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1253},\"output_tokens\":2,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYYZCfz1sipZkaehJttoQ\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"5828d106-9ce4-4d3e-aad0-2b528d8b66a6\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T12:14:56.298Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"5828d106-9ce4-4d3e-aad0-2b528d8b66a6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"d77a9f03-1d5b-4e45-85cd-c5694a211420\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01GdVaYptosGMG395G4o5ePq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01UuK4YFxUHFYzrKNZB1Y9Pw\",\"name\":\"Bash\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"git tag --list 'v0.4.*' --sort=-version:refname | head -10\",\"description\":\"List recent v0.4.x tags\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"s